A customer has a need for a midrange storage solution that provides both block and file
access and requires data space optimization for application volumes and files.
Which solution meets the customers requirements?
A. IBM Storwize V7000 Unified and ACE
B. IBM Storwize V5000
C. IBM Storwize V7000 Unified and Real-time Compression
D. IBM Storwize V7000 Real-time Compression
Answer: C
